text.section:
This subtitle does not apply to:
the Governor;
any unit of the Judicial Branch;
any unit of the Legislative Branch;
the Comptroller of the Treasury;
the inmate adjustment hearing officers;
the Public Service Commission;
the State Workers' Compensation Commission;
the Parole Commission;
the Health Services Cost Review Commission;
the Maryland Health Care Commission; and
unemployment insurance benefit determinations and employer obligation determinations in the Department of Labor, Licensing, and Regulation, and appeals from those determinations.
